OL,3,CTyne Bridge restrictions and closures
OL,4,Cnow in place
OL,6,FLane restrictions are now in place on
OL,7,Fthe Tyne Bridge as a major restoration
OL,8,Fprogramme gets underway in earnest.
OL,10,FClosures from Tuesday 2 April will see
OL,11,Fcapacity halved by up to 70,000
OL,12,Fvehicles a day on one of the routes
OL,13,Fbetween Newcastle and Gateshead.
OL,15,FThe current programme of works will
OL,16,Fsee lane restrictions in place for a
OL,17,Fminimum of two years, with further
OL,18,Ftemporary lane closures and overnight
OL,19,Fclosures scheduled for the remaining
OL,20,Ftwo years of the refurbishment.
