OL,3,CTyne Bridge restrictions and closures
OL,4,Cnow in place
OL,6,FLane restrictions have been started
OL,7,Fduring the school Easter holidays when
OL,8,Ftraffic is lighter which should
OL,9,Finitially minimise the impact on the
OL,10,Ftravelling public but delays and
OL,11,Fcongestion are expected when traffic
OL,12,Freturns to normal levels.
OL,14,FThis could see delays of up to 40
OL,15,Fminutes at peak travel times.
OL,17,FSchedule of restrictions and closures:
OL,19,F2 April: Off-peak lane restrictions
OL,20,Ffrom 9.30am until 3.30pm.
