OL,3,CTyne Bridge restrictions and closures
OL,4,Cnow in place
OL,6,FWith the bridge reduced to one lane in
OL,7,Feach direction to protect the
OL,8,Fworkforce and the public during the
OL,9,Fmain bridge deck restoration, heavy
OL,10,Fcongestion is expected on approaches
OL,11,Fto the Tyne Bridge on both Newcastle
OL,12,Fand Gateshead sides.
OL,14,FThe Quayside is also expected to be
OL,15,Fbusy as people seek to use the Swing
OL,16,FBridge.
OL,18,FThe public is strongly advised to use
OL,19,Fpublic transport where possible when
OL,20,Ftravelling to and from the city centre.
