OL,3,CTyne Bridge restrictions and closures
OL,4,Cnow in place
OL,6,FAs part of the restrictions on the
OL,7,Fbridge, one footway will be available
OL,8,Fat all times.
OL,10,FWalking and cycling routes around the
OL,11,Fbridge are being improved where
OL,12,Fpossible to encourage more people to
OL,13,Fwalk and cycle.
OL,15,FNewcastle City Council is providing
OL,16,Fadditional safe and secure cycle
OL,17,Fstorage in its city centre.
