OL,3,CTyne Bridge restrictions and closures
OL,4,Cnow in place
OL,6,FSeveral improvements have been made to
OL,7,Fthe road network to prioritise buses
OL,8,Fto ease congestion throughout the four-
OL,9,Fyear project.
OL,11,FPeople should also consider Park and
OL,12,FRide sites which can reduce congestion
OL,13,Fand help people get into the centres
OL,14,Fof Newcastle and Gateshead quicker.
