OL,3,CTyne Bridge restrictions and closures
OL,4,Cnow in place
OL,6,FPeople travelling across the region
OL,7,Fare advised to avoid driving through
OL,8,Fthe centre of Newcastle and Gateshead,
OL,9,Fstay on the major trunk roads and use
OL,10,Fother cross-river crossings such as
OL,11,Fthe A1, A19, Tyne Tunnel and Scotswood
OL,12,FBridge.
OL,14,FThe Redheugh Bridge will still be
OL,15,Favailable for cars, but this is also
OL,16,Fexpected to be heavily congested and
OL,17,Fis also subject to weather-related
OL,18,Fclosures, particularly for high-sided
OL,19,Fvehicles in high winds.
