OL,3,CTyne Bridge restrictions and closures
OL,4,Cnow in place
OL,6,FPeople who need to drive into the city
OL,7,Fare advised to consider car sharing,
OL,8,Ftravelling at off-peak times when the
OL,9,Froads are quieter, as well as leaving
OL,10,Fmore time for their journey and to
OL,11,Fexpect delays.
OL,13,FLarge employers are also asked to
OL,14,Fconsider staggering start and finish
OL,15,Ftimes to avoid peak travel times and
OL,16,Fencourage working from home.
