OL,3,CTyne Bridge restrictions and closures
OL,4,Cnow in place
OL,6,FEsh Construction will deliver the
OL,7,Fhugely complex and challenging project
OL,8,Fon behalf of the councils.
OL,10,FOver 900 steelwork repairs have been
OL,11,Fidentified on the Grade II-listed
OL,12,Fstructure, as well as grit blasting
OL,13,Fand re-painting, concrete repairs,
OL,14,Fdrainage improvements, stonework and
OL,15,Fmasonry repairs, bridge deck
OL,16,Fwaterproofing and resurfacing, parapet
OL,17,Fprotection and bridge joint
OL,18,Freplacement.
