OL,3,CTyne Bridge restrictions and closures
OL,4,Cnow in place
OL,6,FThe four-year programme is expected to
OL,7,Fbe complete in Summer 2028, ahead of
OL,8,Fthe bridge's centenary in October 2028.
OL,10,FThe Tyne Bridge restoration is funded
OL,11,Fby the UK Government, as well as
OL,12,Fmonies from both Newcastle City
OL,13,FCouncil and Gateshead Council.
OL,15,FThe Government signed off #35.2
OL,16,Fmillion on 2 February 2024 towards the
OL,17,Fcost of two projects: the restoration
OL,18,Fof the Tyne Bridge and the Central
OL,19,FMotorway upgrade.
